y specific commands or tools (e.g. globs, prefix-only, etc.).\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFunnily enough the code is not vibe coded, almost at all (hence the use of the ai tag instead of vibecoding). I used an agent to generate the initial POC but there's almost 0 agent lines left.\u003c/p\u003e\n","description_plain":"I created a more granular policy-engine for cli agents (at the time of writing only claude code and github copilot cli are supported)\r\n\r\nEach agent implements its own halfway solution to allow/deny specific commands or tools (e.g. globs, prefix-only, etc.).\r\n\r\nFunnily enough the code is not vibe coded, almost at all (hence the use of the ai tag instead of vibecoding). I used an agent to generate the initial POC but there's almost 0 agent lines left.","submitter_user":"dzervas","user_is_author":true,"tags":["vibecoding"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/s4ha0g","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/s4ha0g/mcp_firewall_better_policy_engine_for_cli"},{"short_id":"o1vthu","created_at":"2026-03-01T14:17:43.000-06:00","title":"You don't have to if you don't want to","url":"https://www.scottsmitelli.com/articles/you-dont-have-to/","score":20,"flags":1,"comment_count":6,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"nickmonad","user_is_author":false,"tags":["rant","vibecoding"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/o1vthu","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/o1vthu/you_don_t_have_if_you_don_t_want"},{"short_id":"zuh3zm","created_at":"2026-03-01T13:53:48.000-06:00","title":"qman: A more modern man page viewer for our terminals","url":"https://github.com/plp13/qman","score":46,"flags":0,"comment_count":11,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"dzwdz","user_is_author":false,"tags":["unix"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/zuh3zm","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/zuh3zm/qman_more_modern_man_page_viewer_for_our"},{"short_id":"pf4r2b","created_at":"2026-03-01T13:22:52.000-06:00","title":"AWS Middle East Central Zone (UAE) 